function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	idFollower = Hydra.QuestGetFollower(s_Woodwraith_Follower)
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idFollower) and Hydra.ActorIsAlive(idFollower) then
		Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(idFollower)
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idFollower, false)
		Hydra.ActorSetTargetable(idFollower, false)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idFollower, MARKER_LOCATION_01, "npc_run", true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idFollower, MARKER_LOCATION_01)
		--Hydra.QActorEventSend(idFollower, "QST_Crone_Start_Vignette_01")
		--Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(idFollower, 1.0)
		Hydra.QActorDelete(idFollower)
	end
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	Hydra.QActorSetIdleAnim(id_Woodwraith_Location01, s_POWER_CHANNEL)
	Hydra.QActorWait(id_Woodwraith_Location01, 10.0)
	Hydra.QActorSetIdleAnim(id_Woodwraith_Location01, s_POWER_IDLE)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(id_Woodwraith_Location01)
